\c 13
\s Munyengetero wekukumbira rubatsiro
\p Kumutungamiriri wekuimba; Pisarema raDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Kusvika rinhi Jehovha muchindikanganwa nekusingaperi? Kusvika rinhi muchindivanzira chiso chenyu?
\v 2 Kusvika rinhi ndichiisa zano mumweya wangu, kusuruvara mumoyo mangu zuva nezuva? Kusvika rinhi muvengi wangu achikwiridzirwa pamusoro pangu?
\v 3 Tarisai, ndipindurei, Jehovha Mwari wangu; vhenekerai meso angu, zvimwe ndirare hope dzerufu;
\v 4 zvimwe muvengi wangu at: Ndamukunda; vadzivisi vangu vafare kana ndazununguka.
\v 5 Asi ndakavimba munyasha dzenyu, moyo wangu uchafara nokuponesa kwenyu.
\v 6 Ndichaimbira Jehovha, nokuti akandiitira zvakanaka kwazvo.
